body_html: TensorFlow Lite uses a non-traditional approach for importing and including Eigen, so it's quite possible there are some platform/flag-specific issues that it's not handling properly. See also https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/kernels/internal/optimized/eigen_tensor_reduced_instantiations_oss.h
